00:01:07,470 --> 00:01:08,400
Ty...

6
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,730
Najprv im utečme.

7
00:01:38,460 --> 00:01:39,600
Čo?

8
00:01:39,930 --> 00:01:42,400
